1
00:00:06,980 --> 00:00:10,100
♪I love the clarity in your eyes♪

2
00:00:10,740 --> 00:00:13,860
♪Like a shooting star across my world♪

3
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Repeating the goodbye we never said♪

4
00:00:18,260 --> 00:00:21,540
♪Through sleepless nights♪

5
00:00:21,980 --> 00:00:25,100
♪I miss the way you looked at me♪

6
00:00:25,700 --> 00:00:30,260
♪Like photos freezing that summer bit by bit♪

7
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:35,380
♪By the shore with warm winds, maybe we'll meet again♪

8
00:00:37,380 --> 00:00:41,460
[Fall in Love Again]

9
00:00:41,460 --> 00:00:43,980
[Episode 10]

10
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:47,200
I came back

11
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:49,840
because this place

12
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,240
has someone I can't stop thinking about.

13
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,880
Why is he looking at me?

14
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:57,240
This is so awkward.

15
00:00:58,760 --> 00:00:59,080
Xiwen,

16
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:00,920
come have some coffee.

17
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:02,200
What did you hear?

18
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,230
What did he say?

19
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:07,800
It seemed he came back for someone he cares about.

20
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,800
Still, it has to be a mature man with genuine feelings.

21
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:14,320
Is Mr. Song married?

22
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,640
Of course.

23
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,880
A man this outstanding couldn't be unmarried.

24
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,800
Married and still acting all devoted?

25
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:20,660
Trash!

26
00:01:20,660 --> 00:01:21,180
Trash!

27
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:23,920
Don't talk nonsense.

28
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,520
His wife passed away two years ago.

29
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,640
If you ask me,

30
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:29,120
it still has to be Mr. Song.

31
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,400
Childhood sweethearts.

32
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,440
They've known each other since childhood.

33
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:33,640
And he's gentle and mature.

34
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,760
I've seen so many characters in movies.

35
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:37,320
Not one is as perfect as him.

36
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:39,840
And he solved our company's crisis right after returning.

37
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:41,240
So he and

38
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:43,880
Chu are together?

39
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:46,440
Not before.

40
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,440
But who knows about later.

41
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,720
Who knows about later?

42
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,680
Then they're such a good match.

43
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:56,040
Well, maybe not that well matched.

44
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,040
Stop talking. We can't hear a thing.

45
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,240
That kid just now,

46
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,240
I think he's a bit interested in you.

47
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,520
You said it yourself, he's just a kid.

48
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,800
Besides, I'm not in the mood to think about that now.

49
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:10,910
I just want to focus on my career.

50
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,720
What about you, Xiwen?

51
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,280
Still alone?

52
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,920
It's been so many years since your wife passed away.

53
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,320
Why haven't you found someone else?

54
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,640
Or have you never really let go?

55
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,440
I've already let go.

56
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:31,000
It's just that over the years,

57
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:34,040
I haven't found anyone suitable.

58
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,720
I'm used to being alone.

59
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,840
As if I don't know you.

60
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:40,200
Your standards are probably too high.

61
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,320
You've been like this since you were young.

62
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,840
Other kids would always

63
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,720
choose what to keep and what to give up.

64
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,840
But you're different.

65
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,160
You choose to want it all.

66
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,520
You just told me

67
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,240
that you've always had someone you're thinking about.

68
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,280
Who is it? Do I know them?

69
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:03,840
You do.

70
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,320
And

71
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:06,840
you know her well.

72
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,680
I can't hear a thing.

73
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,260
[Clash of Psychic Beasts]

74
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:20,880
You... you're both here?

75
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,080
Perfect. I was just looking for you.

76
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,120
Go on, go on.

77
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,640
Mr. Song is an important guest of the company.

78
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:27,360
It's more important to host Mr. Song first.

79
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,160
Otherwise, it'll look like we lack sincerity.

80
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,520
All of you, get out!

81
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,800
- Hurry up, go. - Go, hurry.

82
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,640
- Hurry. - Let's go.

83
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:33,840
Hurry up.

84
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,680
He Zheng.

85
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:46,800
Mr. Song

86
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:49,000
has indeed done quite a lot for the company.

87
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:49,480
But you...

88
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:50,400
Mr. Song

89
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:51,520
is really good.

90
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,080
He's not just good.

91
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,680
He also grew up with Chu since childhood.

92
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:58,040
He saved Chu from danger many times.

93
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:58,480
Tell me,

94
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,960
who wouldn't be moved by a man like that?

95
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,040
Our He Zheng has rescued her so many times too.

96
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:04,160
He's no worse than anyone else.

97
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,680
That was just a coincidence.

98
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,480
Because you were there.

99
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,640
It would've been the same for anyone else.

100
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,240
But this time,

101
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,600
if it weren't for Mr. Song,

102
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:13,440
it would've been over.

103
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,480
Who says only Mr. Song could do it?

104
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,000
He Zheng...

105
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,680
I'll always be here.

106
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,800
He's quite devoted.

107
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,640
Xiwen, have some coffee.

108
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:32,800
The coffee's gone.

109
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,680
The water's gone too.

110
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,200
I'll throw up if I drink more.

111
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,240
Alright.

112
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:39,120
By the way.

113
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,720
Um...

114
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,120
In a bit,

115
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:44,600
I'll transfer all the funds under my name to you first.

116
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,400
And the rest?

117
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,600
I can only give you an IOU.

118
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,280
Such a large amount of assets.

119
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,880
How do you plan to repay it?

120
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,240
Don't worry about me.

121
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:53,600
Pressure creates motivation.

122
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,120
I'm...

123
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,480
I'm afraid you won't be able to repay it.

124
00:04:57,720 --> 00:05:00,120
And the money will depreciate.

125
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,720
So this is what you were waiting for.

126
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,600
I'll calculate interest for you, alright?

127
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,480
Xi.

128
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,120
You've matured.

129
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,840
Managing such a big company on your own.

130
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,280
Outstanding.

131
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,320
I'm not on my own.

132
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:21,440
Isn't Yang here too?

133
00:05:24,540 --> 00:05:26,260
[IOU]

134
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:34,200
What does this mean?

135
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,520
No matter how high the interest is, it can't be that much.

136
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:43,320
I prefer investments with higher returns.

137
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:46,040
Consider this money an investment in your company.

138
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,720
How about giving me shares?

139
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,680
Of course.

140
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,840
But this amount of funding is huge.

141
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,480
If you want shares,

142
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,400
then you'll be Origin's largest shareholder.

143
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,680
Don't underestimate yourself.

144
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,680
This company still needs your management and effort.

145
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,080
I just need to be a shareholder,

146
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,400
and wait to collect the money.

147
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:05,120
Okay?

148
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,280
Alright.

149
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,680
Welcome Mr. Song to Origin.

150
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,320
Don't sweet-talk me.

151
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:12,400
If we lose money, I'll hold you accountable.

152
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,400
No problem.

153
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:16,200
Deal.

154
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,280
Happy cooperation.

155
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:33,640
Mr. Song.

156
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,800
How did the check on Mr. Wang go?

157
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,800
It's been found.

158
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:38,880
His personal conduct

159
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:40,440
has serious issues.

160
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:44,340
[Personal Investigation Report]

161
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,920
Because of women,

162
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,640
he made failed decisions

163
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:55,040
and caused the company to lose so much money.

164
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,880
Yet he can still sit in this position.

165
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,120
He had someone else take the blame.

166
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,480
Now EM

167
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,920
still doesn't know whether to expose this.

168
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,480
Let's warn him first.

169
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,880
Come on, take it.

170
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,240
Yu.

171
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,840
The projects I told you about,

172
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,520
I'll take you along on all of them.

173
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:40,120
The roles I promised you,

174
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,200
I'll definitely arrange for you to be in all of them.

175
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:45,640
I give you my word, alright?

176
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:46,240
Come on.

177
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:47,320
Drink.

178
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,560
It's fine. Come on.

179
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:53,720
Come on.

180
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,440
Who is it?

181
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:01,040
I'll go see who it is.

182
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,320
You?

183
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,200
Mr. Wang.

184
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,120
You're just letting her off like that?

185
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:19,600
Do you know how much I paid

186
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,680
to cooperate with you?

187
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,640
That's how business works.

188
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,400
Today you make a move,

189
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,240
tomorrow she loses money.

190
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:30,480
Besides, I didn't lose out on this.

191
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:34,030
First, I got the money.

192
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,150
Second,

193
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,790
I really didn't suffer any losses.

194
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:40,280
Mr. Wang, you're the one who profited.

195
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:43,600
You're not planning to use me like a rag

196
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,600
and toss me aside after that, are you?

197
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,000
Qi.

198
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,880
The grudge between you and Chu Jingxi

199
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,120
is known to everyone.

200
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:54,720
This is nothing more than mutual use between us.

201
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,040
You've achieved your goal.

202
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,120
But I haven't.

203
00:08:59,040 --> 00:08:59,520
Mr. Wang.

204
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,440
We're cooperating.

205
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,640
Isn't this inappropriate?

206
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,120
You also know we're just cooperating?

207
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:08,440
Watch yourself.

208
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,400
Know your place!

209
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:10,480
Watch how you talk to me!

210
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:17,760
I still have some business to handle with Yu.

211
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:19,440
You leave.

212
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:21,920
Yu.

213
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,200
Are you coming with me, or staying here?

214
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:47,720
Qi Siqin.

215
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:50,840
How did I end up drinking so much that day?

216
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:55,680
Listen to me, Yu.

217
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:56,680
I'm sorry.

218
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,440
It was my fault for not taking good care of you that day.

219
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,640
But I swear

220
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:01,880
from today on,

221
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:04,240
I won't let anyone hurt you again.

222
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:08,080
Let's go.

223
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:10,800
Mandy.

224
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,440
The same room.

225
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:14,800
Room 802. I'll wait for you.

226
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,640
I've already sent the driver to pick you up.

227
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:17,720
You have to come.

228
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,480
Yu.

229
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:31,240
Yu, I know you...

230
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,480
[Origin]

231
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,080
Ms. Chu.

232
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:56,480
Do you see anywhere in this contract that still needs revision?

233
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:58,160
The 3-3-4 part still needs revision.

234
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:59,440
From now on, follow the 3-4-3 format.

235
00:10:59,440 --> 00:10:59,920
Alright.

236
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,480
Xi.

237
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:04,080
There were many editors interviewing today.

238
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,000
One of them was pretty good.

239
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:07,200
They're from the former Hualing VFX team.

240
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:09,720
In the future, look for more experienced post-production teams.

241
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,440
Better safe than sorry.

242
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:10,800
Okay.

243
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:14,140
[He Zheng]

244
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,520
[He Zheng]
I'm at the stairwell.

245
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,560
I have something to tell you.

246
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,320
Are you crazy?

247
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,120
This is the office.

248
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,360
Yes, I am crazy.

249
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:44,080
You're all I can think about.

250
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:47,280
Young man, I told you long ago

251
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:48,920
not to waste your time on me.

252
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:50,920
I'm not willing to give up.

253
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,400
You don't hate me, right?

254
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,920
That's right, I don't hate you.

255
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,520
But I don't like you either.

256
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:58,160
You're not the man I want.

257
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:02,920
Don't do anything reckless.

258
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:20,160
I can become the man you want.

259
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,280
What are you two doing here?

260
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:33,880
He Zheng asked me to rehearse with him.

261
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,320
This young guy is quite driven.

262
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,720
I'll prove it to you.

263
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,520
Am I bothering you?

264
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,160
Don't talk nonsense.

265
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,320
What do you need me for?

266
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:51,960
I picked up a few projects.

267
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,360
Let's go over them together.

268
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:54,160
Okay.

269
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,200
Who exactly is trying to target me?

270
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,760
What's his purpose?

271
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:06,280
[ME Media]
This time, let's push hard and win it.

272
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:07,640
Make sure we secure this project.

273
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:08,920
Hello.

274
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:10,760
I'm here to see Mr. Wang from your company.

275
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:12,120
Hello, sir. This way, please.

276
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:12,720
Alright.

277
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,520
If we show up suddenly this time,

278
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:17,080
will Mr. Wang give us the project?

279
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,120
Opportunities have to be fought for.

280
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:20,120
How would we know if we don't try?

281
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:20,600
Alright.

282
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:21,320
Let's go.

283
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:25,520
Mr. Wang.

284
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,000
People from Origin are here.

285
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:28,920
Let them in.

286
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,720
