346
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,080
Alright.

347
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,720
No problem.

348
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:48,360
Mr. Wang.

349
00:15:48,680 --> 00:15:49,520
